verbose_text: MiR-33a overexpression in vitro reduced expression of cholesterol 7alpha hydroxylase (CYP7A1), sterol 12alpha hydroxylase (CYP8B1), sodium-taurocholate cotransporting polypeptide (NTCP), bile salt export pump (BSEP), ATP binding cassette transporter G5 (ABCG5), and ATP binding cassette transporter G8 (ABCG8), all of which are involved in the synthesis and secretion of bile acids in the liver [XREF_BIBR].
